{
  "id": "63eb89c74a7e93001c068ab4",
  "title": "属性ではなく個人",
  "created": 1676380621,
  "updated": 1676381021,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "63eb89c74a7e93001c068ab4",
      "text": "属性ではなく個人",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676380621,
      "updated": 1676380624
    },
    {
      "id": "63eb89d2aff09e0000525fd6",
      "text": "ある嫌われてる人Aが「Xだからあなたが[嫌い]」という発言すべてに「Xという[属性]を理由に人を嫌うのは[差別]だ！」と言った結果、「A[個人]のことが特に理由なく嫌い」に帰着してしまって、かえって救いのない状態にAは自分を追い込んでしまった。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676380626,
      "updated": 1676380903
    },
    {
      "id": "63eb8a66aff09e0000525fd8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676380774,
      "updated": 1676380774
    },
    {
      "id": "63eb8a66aff09e0000525fd9",
      "text": "かわいそうに…",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676380774,
      "updated": 1676380829
    },
    {
      "id": "63eb8ad3aff09e0000525fdb",
      "text": "　だけど自業自得なような…",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676380883,
      "updated": 1676380890
    },
    {
      "id": "63eb8adbaff09e0000525fdc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676380891,
      "updated": 1676380892
    },
    {
      "id": "63eb8a9daff09e0000525fda",
      "text": "どうなればよかったんだろうか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676380830,
      "updated": 1676380839
    },
    {
      "id": "63eb89d6aff09e0000525fd7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676380630,
      "updated": 1676380630
    },
    {
      "id": "63eb8aeaaff09e0000525fdd",
      "text": "「嫌い」のところは抽象化産物",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676380906,
      "updated": 1676380918
    },
    {
      "id": "63eb8af6aff09e0000525fdf",
      "text": "　好き嫌いに限らず人間に対する価値判断がだいたいこれ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676380919,
      "updated": 1676380959
    },
    {
      "id": "63eb8b1eaff09e0000525fe0",
      "text": "　「特に理由はなく私はあなたと会話することが無益だと思っています。」みたいなやつも含む",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676380959,
      "updated": 1676381020
    },
    {
      "id": "63eb8aefaff09e0000525fde",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676380912,
      "updated": 1676380912
    }
  ]
}